N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 8148.17 - Town of Mamakating

State Regulations
(a) [Eff. until Jan. 29, 1992, see also subd. (a) below.] Route 209. Route 209 between

Route 17 and the southerly village line of Wurtsboro, a distance of 0.82+- mile
in the Town of Mamakating. (a) [Eff. Jan. 29, 1992, see also subd. (a) above.] [Repealed]
(b) [Eff. until Jan. 29, 1992, see also subd. (b) below.] Route 209. Route 209
between the northerly village line of Wurtsboro and the Ulster county line, a
distance of 5.68+- miles in the Town of Mamakating. (b) [Eff. Jan. 29, 1992, see also
subd. (b) above.]
[Repealed]
